The '''Hamedan Museum of Natural History''' is a natural history [[museum]] located in the Bu Al Sina University in [[Hamedan]], north-western [[Iran]].
It is noted for its presentation of large horned [[Alborz]] red sheep and a black [[vulture]]. It also has a considerable [[taxidermy|taxidermic]] collection of animals and insects. The museum has an aquarium and live fish tanks.
==External links== *[http://www.bestirantravel.com/sights/hamadan/naturalhistorymuseum.html Best Iran Travel]
