In [[Basque mythology]], '''Odei''', also known as '''Hodei''' is a [[spirit]] of thunder and the personification of storm clouds.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.buber.net/Basque/Folklore/aunamendi.odei.php |title=Basque Mythology: Odei |author=Encyclopedia Auñamendi |date= |work=Buber's Basque Page |accessdate=October 4, 2010}}</ref>

